        series name.
    </p><p>
        This should help with sharing links to the site:
        urls will forward to the new name. If a replacement item is created with the same
        name, the forwarding will stop, and the links will go to the new item.
    </p>
    <p>
        Next up is support for Cox-Sprague scoring: a variant of High Point Percentage.
    </p>
